1
00:01:28,768 --> 00:01:33,760
=Lost You Forever S1=

2
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:36,702
=Episode 38=

3
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:42,219
(I don't want to be Tushan Jing.)

4
00:01:42,940 --> 00:01:45,419
(Whether I can be with you
openly and honorably is not important.)

5
00:01:46,499 --> 00:01:48,419
(Even if I don't get
recognition for a lifetime,)

6
00:01:49,620 --> 00:01:51,300
(even if I'm your servant
for a lifetime,)

7
00:01:51,300 --> 00:01:52,340
(it doesn't matter,)

8
00:01:53,179 --> 00:01:56,580
(I just want to be by your side.)

9
00:02:21,780 --> 00:02:24,220
There are things I can't figure out.

10
00:02:24,980 --> 00:02:26,739
I thought I'd be enlightened

11
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:29,340
during the walk.

12
00:02:30,980 --> 00:02:32,140
Did you figure it out?

13
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:35,060
No.

14
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:38,019
Can you tell me about it?

15
00:02:38,939 --> 00:02:40,860
I don't think we have a say in life.

16
00:02:41,420 --> 00:02:42,620
No matter how powerful we are,

17
00:02:44,459 --> 00:02:45,539
we can't control

18
00:02:45,539 --> 00:02:47,179
the two most important things

19
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:49,060
in life.

20
00:02:50,220 --> 00:02:50,900
Which two?

21
00:02:51,659 --> 00:02:52,220
Life

22
00:02:53,260 --> 00:02:53,860
and death.

23
00:02:54,939 --> 00:02:56,900
We can neither decide how to be born

24
00:02:57,620 --> 00:02:59,739
nor how to die.

25
00:03:01,579 --> 00:03:03,739
If we don't have a say

26
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:05,099
in these two things,

27
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:07,500
I sometimes wonder

28
00:03:07,980 --> 00:03:09,299
why we bother

29
00:03:10,220 --> 00:03:11,780
to fight for and long for

30
00:03:12,299 --> 00:03:13,780
something else.

31
00:03:14,819 --> 00:03:16,179
It's so pointless.

32
00:03:17,429 --> 00:03:22,260
♪I couldn't walk out of the memories♪

33
00:03:22,260 --> 00:03:23,140
You fool.

34
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:25,539
See it from another perspective.

35
00:03:26,099 --> 00:03:28,099
We can't control life and death.

36
00:03:28,939 --> 00:03:30,659
That's exactly why we should

37
00:03:32,140 --> 00:03:33,980
have a say in everything

38
00:03:35,220 --> 00:03:36,539
between life and death.

39
00:03:37,452 --> 00:03:38,719
♪But you are not here tomorrow♪

40
00:03:39,212 --> 00:03:46,494
♪You appear in the rain
but disappear in the water♪

41
00:03:47,998 --> 00:03:49,140
♪You have tears♪

42
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:50,299
I'm tired.

43
00:03:50,299 --> 00:03:51,539
♪In your eyes♪

44
00:03:51,539 --> 00:03:52,700
I'm done walking.

45
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:54,179
We've come this far.

46
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:55,939
Won't you see the view from the peak?

47
00:03:56,539 --> 00:03:58,980
I can carry you if you can't walk.

48
00:04:04,258 --> 00:04:08,539
♪You appear at the end of the river♪

49
00:04:08,539 --> 00:04:10,379
The view is indeed better here.

50
00:04:13,019 --> 00:04:14,459
How do we admire the amazing view

51
00:04:14,819 --> 00:04:16,660
if we don't take
the rugged mountain road?

52
00:04:19,979 --> 00:04:21,660
Tushan Jing.

53
00:04:22,579 --> 00:04:24,179
You broke your promise.

54
00:04:24,620 --> 00:04:27,620
You broke your promise.

55
00:04:29,792 --> 00:04:32,972
♪You appear as the smoke rises♪

56
00:04:33,100 --> 00:04:35,620
Xuan. Find a man for me.

57
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:38,780
What kind of man?

58
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:40,780
Someone to live with.

59
00:04:41,139 --> 00:04:41,940
I don't mind anything,

60
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:44,060
but he can't have another lover.

61
00:04:44,859 --> 00:04:47,220
Otherwise, I'll castrate him.

62
00:04:48,459 --> 00:04:50,139
Maybe Grandfather is right.

63
00:04:51,660 --> 00:04:53,940
It's hard to find the one and only.

64
00:04:54,540 --> 00:04:56,259
But if we choose the right person,

65
00:04:56,620 --> 00:04:57,739
it's not so hard

66
00:04:58,299 --> 00:04:59,299
to respect each other

67
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:01,139
and live together for life.

68
00:05:01,259 --> 00:05:03,060
I no longer trust my judgment.

69
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:05,739
Choose for me.

70
00:05:06,859 --> 00:05:07,380
Alright.

71
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:10,139
I'll choose for you.

72
00:05:10,979 --> 00:05:12,139
If he lets you down,

73
00:05:12,900 --> 00:05:14,100
I'll kill him

74
00:05:14,699 --> 00:05:15,979
before you castrate him.

75
00:05:20,299 --> 00:05:22,100
I know I can count on you.

76
00:05:45,419 --> 00:05:45,900
Father.

77
00:05:53,540 --> 00:05:55,220
Your Majesty. Time for medicine.

78
00:06:04,419 --> 00:06:09,179
Those memorials are handed in
to impeach Cang Xuan?

79
00:06:09,820 --> 00:06:10,340
Yes.

80
00:06:10,459 --> 00:06:11,019
Father.

81
00:06:12,019 --> 00:06:13,340
Cang Xuan married Miss Shen

82
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:15,979
and started forming alliances
to establish influence,

83
00:06:16,579 --> 00:06:18,299
which displeased the old clans of Xiyan.

84
00:06:18,660 --> 00:06:21,579
Even some local clans found it unacceptable

85
00:06:21,739 --> 00:06:22,739
and handed in reports.

86
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:25,579
These are the accusations.

87
00:06:25,979 --> 00:06:27,060
Please take a look.

88
00:06:33,620 --> 00:06:35,299
You've always prevented those clans

89
00:06:35,299 --> 00:06:36,699
from forming alliances,

90
00:06:37,019 --> 00:06:38,940
so that they don't group up against us.

91
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:40,620
But Cang Xuan

92
00:06:40,699 --> 00:06:42,299
is doing the opposite

93
00:06:42,859 --> 00:06:44,179
and mingling with them.

94
00:06:44,699 --> 00:06:45,380
I'm afraid

95
00:06:47,139 --> 00:06:48,019
someone may use him

96
00:06:48,579 --> 00:06:49,780
as a disguise

97
00:06:50,419 --> 00:06:52,259
to set up an independent regime.

98
00:06:52,459 --> 00:06:56,220
Since you've investigated everything,

99
00:06:56,979 --> 00:07:00,500
I won't read the memorials.

100
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:18,060
The palace
on Chenrong Mountain is completed.

101
00:07:18,660 --> 00:07:20,859
I intend to visit the Central Plains

102
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:22,780
and ascend the Zijin Peak

103
00:07:23,139 --> 00:07:24,620
to worship heaven and earth.

104
00:07:26,579 --> 00:07:28,380
Your Majesty, please think twice.

105
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:30,620
Although all the clans

106
00:07:30,699 --> 00:07:32,060
have submitted to you,

107
00:07:32,259 --> 00:07:34,060
they're not our kind.

108
00:07:34,340 --> 00:07:35,340
We can't trust them.

109
00:07:36,019 --> 00:07:37,579
There was an assassination

110
00:07:37,620 --> 00:07:39,060
during your previous trip.

111
00:07:39,419 --> 00:07:41,139
If you visit the Central Plains,

112
00:07:41,139 --> 00:07:43,380
some sinister people

113
00:07:43,500 --> 00:07:45,859
may try to launch another attack.

114
00:07:46,299 --> 00:07:48,579
I've been ruling
the Central Plains for years.

115
00:07:49,299 --> 00:07:51,699
If someone harbors evil designs

116
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:53,179
and wants to rebel,

117
00:07:53,739 --> 00:07:56,259
I will happily take them down.

118
00:07:57,259 --> 00:07:58,859
The law of heaven is written.

119
00:07:59,299 --> 00:08:00,859
Fate is not easily changed.

120
00:08:01,419 --> 00:08:02,940
We hope that virtues

121
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:04,780
will preside over Dahuang.

122
00:08:05,179 --> 00:08:06,739
In mid-spring,

123
00:08:06,940 --> 00:08:08,540
head to the Central Plains

124
00:08:08,940 --> 00:08:10,579
and ascend Chenrong Mountain

125
00:08:10,859 --> 00:08:12,299
to worship heaven and earth.

126
00:08:12,699 --> 00:08:14,459
Pay tribute to all gods and deities

127
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:16,299
and pacify all rivers and lakes.

128
00:08:16,780 --> 00:08:19,579
Xiyan Deyan is made

129
00:08:19,859 --> 00:08:21,699
envoy of the journey

130
00:08:21,940 --> 00:08:23,500
to keep His Majesty company.

131
00:08:24,220 --> 00:08:25,500
Xiyan Yuyang

132
00:08:25,739 --> 00:08:27,060
and General Yinglong

133
00:08:27,259 --> 00:08:29,220
will stay in Xiyan Town

134
00:08:29,459 --> 00:08:31,179
and assist in state affairs.

135
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:34,379
Your Majesty, you are truly wise.

136
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,740
(Zezhou)

137
00:09:04,740 --> 00:09:05,980
For hundreds of years,

138
00:09:06,660 --> 00:09:09,459
our Xiyan Kingdom hasn't had any wars.

139
00:09:10,459 --> 00:09:11,980
But our soldiers

140
00:09:12,259 --> 00:09:13,780
practice day and night

141
00:09:14,059 --> 00:09:16,340
without any days off.

142
00:09:17,180 --> 00:09:20,699
I invited you
to review troops with me today.

143
00:09:21,259 --> 00:09:24,660
How do you feel about it?

144
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:26,780
They stick to the letter of the law.

145
00:09:27,540 --> 00:09:28,259
Very good.

146
00:09:28,420 --> 00:09:30,780
Very good.

147
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:32,180
Father's fierce troops

148
00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:34,059
will triumph over

149
00:09:34,220 --> 00:09:35,300
any foreign intruders

150
00:09:35,660 --> 00:09:37,379
or domestic rebels

151
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:38,819
without a doubt.

152
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:42,139
This troop review is not a show-off.

153
00:09:42,660 --> 00:09:44,819
It's meant to show you

154
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:48,059
that you can rest assured
and live in peace

155
00:09:48,180 --> 00:09:52,100
with our soldiers defending the kingdom.

156
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:55,300
Your Majesty, you're truly wise.

157
00:09:55,499 --> 00:09:57,220
It's a blessing for the people.

158
00:09:57,459 --> 00:09:58,860
You may all rise.

159
00:09:59,819 --> 00:10:00,819
Tomorrow,

160
00:10:01,019 --> 00:10:03,420
I will hold a feast in Zezhou

161
00:10:04,259 --> 00:10:06,579
to share a few drinks with you.

162
00:10:07,499 --> 00:10:09,300
Thank you, Your Majesty.

163
00:10:13,499 --> 00:10:14,139
Your Majesty.

164
00:10:14,819 --> 00:10:16,660
Prince Cang Xuan is here.

165
00:10:17,139 --> 00:10:18,980
Would you like to see him?

166
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:22,379
I don't need his company.

167
00:10:22,780 --> 00:10:25,340
Tell him to stay on Chenrong Mountain.

168
00:10:26,819 --> 00:10:28,259
And the feast tomorrow?

169
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:29,632
He doesn't have to come.

170
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:36,300
(Sifang Hall)
Understood.

171
00:10:45,980 --> 00:10:48,019
His Majesty has refused
to see you many times.

172
00:10:48,420 --> 00:10:50,059
He's clearly distancing himself.

173
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:54,740
Let's go back.

174
00:10:55,220 --> 00:10:55,780
Your Highness.

175
00:11:02,619 --> 00:11:03,579
The King of Xiyan

176
00:11:03,579 --> 00:11:04,819
is holding a feast in Zezhou.

177
00:11:05,579 --> 00:11:07,220
Chenrong Mountain is right there.

178
00:11:07,459 --> 00:11:08,660
But he refused

179
00:11:08,660 --> 00:11:09,900
to see Cang Xuan many times.

180
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:11,900
Everyone knows that he's trying

181
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:13,100
to suppress Cang Xuan.

182
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:14,660
Once he makes up his mind,

183
00:11:15,379 --> 00:11:17,819
Cang Xuan may be in danger.

184
00:11:24,420 --> 00:11:24,980
Qin Mang,

185
00:11:25,619 --> 00:11:27,220
head to Xiyan Town now

186
00:11:27,660 --> 00:11:29,860
and give it to General Yinglong.

187
00:11:31,540 --> 00:11:32,100
Ru Shou,

188
00:11:32,220 --> 00:11:33,540
go to Chenrong Mountain

189
00:11:33,660 --> 00:11:35,019
and get Xiaoyao and Nian back.

190
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:37,340
Yes.

191
00:11:49,019 --> 00:11:50,019
Don't touch anything.

192
00:11:57,019 --> 00:11:57,699
Sister.

193
00:11:59,939 --> 00:12:02,019
The King of Xiyan
has come to the Central Plains.

194
00:12:02,019 --> 00:12:04,540
Why doesn't he meet Xuan?

195
00:12:05,019 --> 00:12:06,499
Is he still mad at him?

196
00:12:08,860 --> 00:12:09,740
How can it be?

197
00:12:10,019 --> 00:12:11,139
Cang Xuan built

198
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:13,740
the palace
on Chenrong Mountain very well.

199
00:12:14,180 --> 00:12:15,660
That's why the king came.

200
00:12:15,900 --> 00:12:17,019
How can he be mad?

201
00:12:17,900 --> 00:12:18,540
That's good.

202
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:23,499
Princess.

203
00:12:23,660 --> 00:12:24,619
Ru Shou is here.

204
00:12:30,939 --> 00:12:32,740
Master has something urgent
to discuss with you.

205
00:12:33,139 --> 00:12:35,139
Please come back with me now.

206
00:12:35,379 --> 00:12:36,420
What's so urgent?

207
00:12:37,019 --> 00:12:38,819
Is he picking a husband for me again?

208
00:12:39,379 --> 00:12:40,980
Maybe. Maybe not.

209
00:12:41,499 --> 00:12:42,499
You will find out.

210
00:12:44,379 --> 00:12:45,420
Tell Father

211
00:12:45,699 --> 00:12:47,340
that I can't go back yet.

212
00:12:47,860 --> 00:12:48,939
He will understand.

213
00:12:50,220 --> 00:12:51,420
Take Nian back with you.

214
00:12:52,259 --> 00:12:52,740
Sister.

215
00:12:53,180 --> 00:12:54,660
Why can't you come yet?

216
00:12:55,980 --> 00:12:58,660
The King of Xiyan
will ascend the Chenrong Mountain.

217
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:00,379
I haven't greeted him

218
00:13:00,579 --> 00:13:01,740
as his granddaughter.

219
00:13:02,019 --> 00:13:03,259
How can I leave now?

220
00:13:04,619 --> 00:13:05,180
True.

221
00:13:05,900 --> 00:13:07,740
Good girl. Leave.

222
00:13:08,579 --> 00:13:10,100
I'll be back once I make things clear

223
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:10,660
with Father.

224
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:11,740
Alright.

225
00:13:24,379 --> 00:13:26,259
Great Princess, take care.

226
00:13:27,540 --> 00:13:28,340
I will.

227
00:13:47,379 --> 00:13:47,980
Be careful.

228
00:13:48,660 --> 00:13:50,059
Master is worried about you.

229
00:13:50,379 --> 00:13:52,340
He sent Ru Shou
to take you back to Wushen Mountain.

230
00:13:52,340 --> 00:13:53,699
Why didn't you go back?

231
00:13:55,459 --> 00:13:56,699
Didn't we have a deal?

232
00:13:57,420 --> 00:13:59,980
We leave or stay together.

233
00:14:03,019 --> 00:14:04,459
You'll be in danger if you stay.

234
00:14:05,459 --> 00:14:07,459
Grandfather invited
all those clans in Zezhou.

235
00:14:08,139 --> 00:14:09,860
Both Fenglong and Xinyue got invited,

236
00:14:09,980 --> 00:14:10,980
but not me.

237
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:12,900
Grandfather is suspecting me

238
00:14:12,900 --> 00:14:14,100
due to my uncles' slander.

239
00:14:14,819 --> 00:14:15,980
Can you deal with it?

240
00:14:16,300 --> 00:14:17,180
Of course, I can.

241
00:14:17,459 --> 00:14:18,860
Then don't drive me away.

242
00:14:20,499 --> 00:14:21,220
Okay, to be honest.

243
00:14:21,780 --> 00:14:22,139
No.

244
00:14:22,459 --> 00:14:23,220
So I can't leave.

245
00:14:24,019 --> 00:14:25,300
You need my protection and support.

246
00:14:26,220 --> 00:14:27,379
Xiaoyao, I beg you.

247
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:28,939
Leave.

248
00:14:29,619 --> 00:14:31,499
Chenrong Mountain is dangerous now.

249
00:14:35,780 --> 00:14:36,939
No need to worry about me.

250
00:14:38,300 --> 00:14:39,300
I'm not my mother.

251
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:42,139
King of Xiyan never raised me.

252
00:14:46,019 --> 00:14:47,699
If he dares to come after us,

253
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:51,220
I will fight back.

254
00:14:59,459 --> 00:15:00,860
He raised you for decades.

255
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:02,459
If things go wrong

256
00:15:03,059 --> 00:15:05,660
and you can't do it, leave it to me.

257
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:16,672
(Zezhou Residence)

258
00:15:33,019 --> 00:15:35,939
Your Majesty, it's been tiring
for you to hold feasts

259
00:15:36,139 --> 00:15:37,540
and meet the clan chiefs

260
00:15:37,939 --> 00:15:38,980
these days.

261
00:15:39,420 --> 00:15:41,900
Please take the medicine and go to bed.

262
00:15:54,059 --> 00:15:54,980
Assassins!

263
00:16:16,459 --> 00:16:17,740
Keep them alive.

264
00:16:26,340 --> 00:16:27,459
- I failed to keep you safe.
- I failed to keep you safe.

265
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:28,860
- I deserve any punishment.
- I deserve any punishment.

266
00:16:30,139 --> 00:16:31,220
Investigate it.

267
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:32,900
Understood.

268
00:16:45,300 --> 00:16:45,860
How did it go?

269
00:16:47,340 --> 00:16:48,420
Your Majesty.

270
00:16:48,740 --> 00:16:50,139
There are ten assassins.

271
00:16:50,540 --> 00:16:52,579
Two of them have tattoos.

272
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:54,660
The patterns are ordinary,

273
00:16:54,860 --> 00:16:56,939
but they were tattooed with Ruomu syrup.

274
00:16:57,340 --> 00:16:59,540
You can tell how old the tattoos are.

275
00:17:00,259 --> 00:17:03,300
Have you checked them?

276
00:17:03,499 --> 00:17:05,259
I've inspected them.

277
00:17:06,099 --> 00:17:07,379
The tattoos

278
00:17:08,139 --> 00:17:10,339
are at least 30 years old.

279
00:17:12,219 --> 00:17:14,060
Ruomu is the sacred tree

280
00:17:14,940 --> 00:17:16,339
of the Ruoshui Clan.

281
00:17:17,019 --> 00:17:17,900
It's heavily guarded,

282
00:17:18,540 --> 00:17:20,099
so ordinary people can't approach it.

283
00:17:21,499 --> 00:17:23,339
Our aunt was the chief
of the Ruoshui Clan.

284
00:17:23,619 --> 00:17:24,460
After she passed away,

