565
00:32:14,619 --> 00:32:15,619
Thank you, Grandfather.

566
00:32:37,019 --> 00:32:39,700
Xiaoyao usually looks easygoing.

567
00:32:40,660 --> 00:32:41,900
But she's really sharp.

568
00:32:42,099 --> 00:32:43,580
It was such a tricky question

569
00:32:44,099 --> 00:32:45,580
that Deyan began to stagger.

570
00:32:45,619 --> 00:32:45,940
You...

571
00:32:46,460 --> 00:32:46,780
You...

572
00:32:48,180 --> 00:32:49,739
She's so articulate.

573
00:32:50,460 --> 00:32:51,780
If someone marries her,

574
00:32:52,259 --> 00:32:53,420
he has to lay low

575
00:32:54,859 --> 00:32:56,180
to avoid any fights.

576
00:33:01,940 --> 00:33:03,660
They kind of passed a test today.

577
00:33:04,019 --> 00:33:05,379
It calls for a celebration

578
00:33:05,499 --> 00:33:07,060
over fine wine in Zhiyi.

579
00:33:09,700 --> 00:33:12,460
I'm afraid that
it won't be easy to leave.

580
00:33:13,979 --> 00:33:14,979
What do you mean?

581
00:33:24,180 --> 00:33:25,019
Your Majesty.

582
00:34:25,299 --> 00:34:26,740
I heard about the assassination

583
00:34:27,819 --> 00:34:28,700
and came to visit.

584
00:34:29,260 --> 00:34:30,339
Since you're all well,

585
00:34:30,740 --> 00:34:31,900
we shall let you rest.

586
00:34:32,099 --> 00:34:34,539
I heard you're
the best chess player in Dahuang.

587
00:34:35,420 --> 00:34:36,700
Since you're here,

588
00:34:37,059 --> 00:34:38,740
play a set with me.

589
00:34:42,059 --> 00:34:42,420
Yes.

590
00:35:06,859 --> 00:35:07,339
Be careful.

591
00:35:16,619 --> 00:35:17,900
You'll defend. I'll attack.

592
00:35:33,940 --> 00:35:34,460
Well done.

593
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:35,940
My spirit power
is enough for three shots.

594
00:35:35,940 --> 00:35:36,660
That's enough.

595
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:30,099
The arrow is poisoned.

596
00:36:43,539 --> 00:36:45,859
You're really outperforming your master.

597
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:53,700
This is the last shot.

598
00:36:54,260 --> 00:36:55,700
Grandfather lives behind that.

599
00:36:55,859 --> 00:36:56,900
I was thinking the same thing.

600
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:28,940
Assassins!

601
00:37:30,059 --> 00:37:31,660
I shall take your life next time.

602
00:37:35,900 --> 00:37:36,339
Your Majesty.

603
00:37:36,619 --> 00:37:37,460
There are assassins.

604
00:37:37,579 --> 00:37:39,099
We came to your protection.

605
00:37:56,500 --> 00:37:57,700
You may be busy.

606
00:37:58,180 --> 00:37:59,020
I shall take my leave.

607
00:37:59,500 --> 00:38:00,460
I shall take my leave.

608
00:38:02,260 --> 00:38:02,980
Go.

609
00:38:13,859 --> 00:38:14,660
Not bad.

610
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:16,980
Using someone's strength
against himself.

611
00:38:24,539 --> 00:38:25,220
General, have you

612
00:38:25,220 --> 00:38:26,740
seen Prince Cang Xuan and Princess?

613
00:38:26,940 --> 00:38:29,020
They have left safe and sound.

614
00:38:32,980 --> 00:38:34,339
So smart.

615
00:38:35,260 --> 00:38:37,220
She managed to escape
from Fifth King's trap

616
00:38:37,660 --> 00:38:38,940
and caused him some trouble.

617
00:38:38,980 --> 00:38:39,539
Yeah.

618
00:38:39,900 --> 00:38:41,180
Cang Xuan is so impressive.

619
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:43,900
He created something out of nothing

620
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:45,859
and planted evidence
to frame the culprit

621
00:38:45,859 --> 00:38:47,420
with a crafty escape plan.

622
00:38:48,660 --> 00:38:49,859
Let's get out of the city.

623
00:38:50,020 --> 00:38:51,500
We may still catch up with them.

624
00:38:53,900 --> 00:38:54,339
Alright.

625
00:38:55,083 --> 00:38:57,948
(Zezhou)

626
00:39:01,579 --> 00:39:02,460
I can't wait anymore.

627
00:39:03,619 --> 00:39:04,420
Get ready.

628
00:39:04,779 --> 00:39:05,700
Gather the people.

629
00:39:06,299 --> 00:39:07,339
Save His Highness.

630
00:39:11,779 --> 00:39:12,539
Your Highness.

631
00:39:18,500 --> 00:39:19,700
Sorry I made you worry.

632
00:39:22,059 --> 00:39:23,180
Why did you come?

633
00:39:30,339 --> 00:39:31,339
I toast you

634
00:39:31,819 --> 00:39:33,500
with water as wine.

635
00:39:33,500 --> 00:39:35,579
Thank you for coming to my rescue.

636
00:39:35,940 --> 00:39:36,900
Don't mention it.

637
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:38,779
Fenglong insisted on it.

638
00:39:38,900 --> 00:39:40,339
I only companied him here.

639
00:39:40,619 --> 00:39:42,819
Besides, I didn't really help.

640
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:46,700
Thankfully, you're safe.

641
00:39:46,819 --> 00:39:47,819
We're brothers.

642
00:39:48,220 --> 00:39:49,260
I'll stop the cliché.

643
00:39:57,420 --> 00:39:58,379
Let me toast you

644
00:39:58,539 --> 00:39:59,299
with water too.

645
00:40:01,059 --> 00:40:02,299
Your escape plan

646
00:40:02,379 --> 00:40:03,740
deserves a nice pot of wine.

647
00:40:03,940 --> 00:40:05,099
We'll do it another time.

648
00:40:05,299 --> 00:40:06,619
All thanks to the person

649
00:40:06,619 --> 00:40:08,180
who came up with the sneaky plan.

650
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:15,940
You're the one who planned it?

651
00:40:16,420 --> 00:40:17,700
That's right.

652
00:40:46,379 --> 00:40:47,859
Chief Tushan, thanks for coming

653
00:40:48,220 --> 00:40:49,180
to our rescue.

654
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:12,900
See you around.

655
00:41:17,059 --> 00:41:18,020
See you around.

656
00:41:18,220 --> 00:41:19,139
Stay alert.

657
00:41:43,900 --> 00:41:44,420
Jing.

658
00:41:45,299 --> 00:41:46,339
May I talk to you?

659
00:41:47,619 --> 00:41:48,940
Xiaoyao...

660
00:41:51,819 --> 00:41:52,779
Xiaoyao...

661
00:41:53,420 --> 00:41:54,220
I think...

662
00:41:57,099 --> 00:41:58,900
If you truly like her,

663
00:41:59,980 --> 00:42:01,379
I have no right to object.

664
00:42:03,779 --> 00:42:04,539
Jing.

665
00:42:05,900 --> 00:42:07,220
I feel sorry

666
00:42:07,900 --> 00:42:09,339
that I like Xiaoyao.

667
00:42:10,900 --> 00:42:12,460
I wouldn't have done this if you hadn't

668
00:42:12,500 --> 00:42:13,660
gotten married and gotten a kid.

669
00:42:14,139 --> 00:42:15,020
I understand.

670
00:42:16,220 --> 00:42:17,420
Xiaoyao is a good girl.

671
00:42:18,619 --> 00:42:19,819
I also hope that

672
00:42:19,819 --> 00:42:20,900
she can find someone

673
00:42:22,220 --> 00:42:23,579
who loves her and deserves her.

674
00:42:25,248 --> 00:42:29,295
♪I failed to meet your gaze♪

675
00:42:30,816 --> 00:42:33,819
♪Only emptiness remained♪

676
00:42:33,819 --> 00:42:34,940
Miao Pu said that

677
00:42:35,500 --> 00:42:36,740
Shen Shutong left

678
00:42:36,740 --> 00:42:38,299
after we came back.

679
00:42:39,020 --> 00:42:41,220
No wonder people want
connection by marriage.

680
00:42:41,539 --> 00:42:42,700
At this critical moment,

681
00:42:43,099 --> 00:42:44,299
only the Shen family

682
00:42:44,539 --> 00:42:46,099
would dare to come and visit.

683
00:42:46,980 --> 00:42:48,500
Grandfather is worried because

684
00:42:49,059 --> 00:42:50,660
the clans of the Central Plains

685
00:42:50,779 --> 00:42:52,619
are all connected by marriage.

686
00:42:54,220 --> 00:42:55,700
When are you going to marry Xinyue?

687
00:42:56,660 --> 00:42:57,900
If you get married,

688
00:42:58,339 --> 00:42:59,819
we have a better chance.

689
00:43:00,779 --> 00:43:02,260
It's not up to me.

690
00:43:03,099 --> 00:43:04,539
Right now,

691
00:43:04,859 --> 00:43:06,339
she wouldn't even see me,

692
00:43:06,579 --> 00:43:07,660
let alone marry me.

693
00:43:08,379 --> 00:43:10,099
Apart from you silly girl,

694
00:43:11,139 --> 00:43:13,500
people only help me
to get things they want.

695
00:43:15,059 --> 00:43:15,819
Do you feel bad?

696
00:43:16,180 --> 00:43:17,420
Why would I?

697
00:43:18,700 --> 00:43:19,900
Life is hard for everyone.

698
00:43:20,619 --> 00:43:21,500
Shouldn't we

699
00:43:21,500 --> 00:43:22,460
think for ourselves?

700
00:43:24,260 --> 00:43:26,059
Love is not everything in life.

701
00:43:26,379 --> 00:43:27,900
You can't feed on it

702
00:43:28,379 --> 00:43:30,020
and warm yourself with it.

703
00:43:30,779 --> 00:43:32,579
Not many people have unconditional love.

704
00:43:33,339 --> 00:43:34,779
Xinyue seems to be demanding,

705
00:43:35,420 --> 00:43:36,740
but she also offers a lot.

706
00:43:37,420 --> 00:43:38,420
I give her what she wants.

707
00:43:38,579 --> 00:43:39,539
Vice versa.

708
00:43:40,379 --> 00:43:41,020
It's fair.

709
00:43:42,819 --> 00:43:43,980
I'm glad you got over it.

710
00:43:45,299 --> 00:43:46,579
Have I ever been troubled?

711
00:43:47,740 --> 00:43:48,940
You're the troubled one.

712
00:43:50,579 --> 00:43:51,339
Yeah.

713
00:43:51,500 --> 00:43:53,099
That's the way it is in this world.

714
00:43:53,619 --> 00:43:55,020
But people are greedy.

715
00:43:55,940 --> 00:43:56,859
I just hope that

716
00:43:57,260 --> 00:43:58,940
you can be unique

717
00:43:59,099 --> 00:44:00,660
to Xinyue.

718
00:44:00,940 --> 00:44:01,619
That's enough.

719
00:44:02,059 --> 00:44:03,099
I don't care at all.

720
00:44:03,779 --> 00:44:04,500
Besides,

721
00:44:04,500 --> 00:44:05,900
she's not unique to me, either.

722
00:44:06,539 --> 00:44:09,020
Why do I get to ask her
to find me unique?

723
00:44:10,099 --> 00:44:11,579
Stop feeling aggrieved for me.

724
00:44:16,660 --> 00:44:17,660
Hop on. Piggyback.

725
00:44:20,220 --> 00:44:21,539
For real?

726
00:44:22,859 --> 00:44:23,940
You think I'm kidding?

727
00:44:24,379 --> 00:44:25,260
I said piggyback.

728
00:44:26,700 --> 00:44:27,700
Alright, alright.

729
00:44:27,700 --> 00:44:28,779
You offered it.

730
00:44:29,420 --> 00:44:30,619
Let's go home.

731
00:44:33,339 --> 00:44:34,819
Why don't you want piggyback now?

732
00:44:35,700 --> 00:44:38,220
Who was the kid that made me
carry her to save her from walking?

733
00:44:40,859 --> 00:44:41,500
Fine.

734
00:44:41,819 --> 00:44:43,020
Since you don't mind,

735
00:44:43,180 --> 00:44:44,099
why would I mind?

736
00:44:44,099 --> 00:44:48,819
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

737
00:44:48,819 --> 00:44:49,379
Let's go.

738
00:44:49,664 --> 00:44:56,319
♪Everything seems sad,
while only your brows raise in delight♪

739
00:44:56,736 --> 00:45:01,795
♪I'm waiting for you
to enjoy the scenery at night♪

740
00:45:01,795 --> 00:45:05,700
♪You came with wind and rain,
while left with my four seasons♪

741
00:45:05,700 --> 00:45:06,299
Xuan.

742
00:45:08,059 --> 00:45:09,819
We must live a good life.

743
00:45:14,059 --> 00:45:14,460
Alright.

744
00:45:14,460 --> 00:45:21,792
♪It began like a tornado,
and went away leaving only dust♪

745
00:45:23,552 --> 00:45:35,872
♪Without you,
even the most beautiful world is a mess♪

746
00:45:53,344 --> 00:45:58,400
♪I offered up my prayers in this life♪

747
00:45:58,528 --> 00:46:04,032
♪For forever accompanying you♪

748
00:46:04,320 --> 00:46:10,125
♪I brewed eternal yearning in wines♪

749
00:46:10,125 --> 00:46:15,808
♪Walking in the mortal with you♪

750
00:46:16,768 --> 00:46:21,760
♪I offered up my prayers
in the next life♪

751
00:46:21,891 --> 00:46:27,168
♪For our permanent love to continue♪

752
00:46:27,634 --> 00:46:33,473
♪Let momentary sorrow and joy fly♪

753
00:46:33,628 --> 00:46:39,520
♪Till the end of the world,
I'll hold you♪

754
00:46:40,155 --> 00:46:45,216
♪The fate brought us to here♪

755
00:46:45,376 --> 00:46:51,136
♪I almost forgot about
the first time I met you♪

756
00:46:51,880 --> 00:46:56,704
♪The destiny brought us together♪

757
00:46:56,998 --> 00:47:02,783
♪I would drink with you
in our limited life♪

758
00:47:03,008 --> 00:47:08,768
♪Under a crescent moon,
I felt empty and emotional♪

759
00:47:08,768 --> 00:47:14,560
♪Afraid I would lost you forever
with mixed feelings♪

760
00:47:14,560 --> 00:47:20,651
♪Hope your eyes remain pure and warm
and our country splendid♪

761
00:47:20,811 --> 00:47:26,240
♪I prefer mortal life,
enjoying abundant blossoms♪

762
00:47:26,240 --> 00:47:32,192
♪Under a crescent moon,
I felt empty and emotional♪

763
00:47:32,192 --> 00:47:38,016
♪Afraid I would lost you forever
with mixed feelings♪

764
00:47:38,016 --> 00:47:45,760
♪Hope your eyes remain pure and warm
and our country splendid♪

765
